\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf2 \cb3 The structure of a WordPress block theme revolves around several key components that work together to create a flexible and customizable design:\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa398\partightenfactor0

