\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 ACF Blocks improves block themes by letting you ship {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://react.dev/"}}{\fldrslt \cb3 \ul React}}-rendered Gutenberg blocks with the familiar PHP templating you already know, collapsing days of JavaScript-heavy work into a single morning\'92s sprint.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa400\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs40 \cf2 \cb3 5. Use the Site Editor to test and fine-tune\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf2 \cb3 With your templates in place, use the Site Editor to preview, edit, and adjust layouts visually.\cb1 \
\cb3 In the WP admin dashboard, go to 
\f3\i Appearance > Editor
\f1\i0 , then open a template and preview how it renders with real content.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf5 {{\NeXTGraphic 39174f8297c72aa9d3078caa630fb41e8b14e5af52c0f71a788901813a2e57e4.png \width16220 \height13040 \appleattachmentpadding0 \appleembedtype0 \appleaqc
}¬}\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\pard\pardeftab720\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 Use the block inspector to change spacing, alignment, font sizes, and other style settings. Use the 
\f3\i Global Styles
\f1\i0  panel to edit site-wide settings, such as fonts, colors, and layout.\cb1 \
\cb3 Save your changes when you\'92re done \'96 WordPress writes them to the corresponding .html files if you want to review them. If changes don\'92t apply, check 
\f3\i theme.json
\f1\i0  or re-save templates in the editor.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa400\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs40 \cf2 \cb3 6. Deploy the theme\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf2 \cb3 Once your theme is ready, you can install it on live sites or distribute it to others:\cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf2 \cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	1	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Go to your theme folder and compress it into a 
\f3\i .zip
\f1\i0  file.\cb1 \
\ls8\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	2	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Log in to the WordPress admin of your target site.\cb1 \
\ls8\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	3	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Go to 
\f3\i Appearance > Themes > Add New > Upload Theme
\f1\i0 .\cb1 \
\ls8\ilvl0\cb3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	4	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Upload the 
\f3\i .zip
\f1\i0 , install, and activate it.\cb1 \
